type: software
title: "Agent Conversation Explorer"
abstract: >
  A React + TypeScript tool for browsing and debugging live agent conversations
  via Azure Application Insights telemetry. Visualises conversation transcripts,
  Copilot Studio execution paths, and error logs from Power Virtual Agents /
  Copilot Studio bots.
